counter = 0
error_counter = 0

for (i in 1:length(dl)) {
  api_url <- paste0(base, key, page)
  retreive_api <- get(api_url)
  
  if(status_code(retreive_api) == 404)
    {
      error_counter = error_counter + 1
      json_info <- data.frame(

        # columnName = 'NA'

  else
  {

}
